title: Here's the USWNT's roster (and cuts) for the SheBelieves Cup
text:
Feb 24, 2017 at 4:58p ET 0Shares 
The U.S. women's national team is hosting the SheBelieves Cup vs. Germany, France and England next week and Jill Ellis named her 23-woman roster for the tournament on Friday. Here is the roster, plus which players got cut. John David Mercer John David Mercer-USA TODAY Spor Jane Campbell (Houston Dash) 
USA TODAY Sports Jonathan Dyer Ashlyn Harris (Orlando Pride) Alyssa Naeher (Chicago Red Stars) 
Kyle Terada Kyle Terada-USA TODAY Sports Julie Johnston (Chicago Red Stars) 
Getty Images Pedro Vilela
